          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The astrophysical S-factor of 3He(p,g)7Be reaction",
                "was determined at the solar Gamow peak by using",
                "experimentally measured solar neutrino fluxes from",
                "Borexino and SNO.",
                " (1) The 3He(a,g)7Be reaction rate was modified from",
                " the value in the solar standard model so that the",
                " 7Be and 8B neutrino fluxes calculated with the",
                " solar standard model parameter set reproduces the",
                " measured 7Be and 8Be neutrino fluxes.",
                " (2) The S-factor at the solar energy (23 keV) was",
                " rescaled by relating the adjusted reaction rate",
                " and S-factor by \"Solar Fusion II\" parametrization.",
                " (3) The S-factor at zero energy was determined from",
                " the 23 keV S-factors from this work and",
                " experimental S-factors assuming that the \"Solar",
                " Fusion II\" functional form."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "RRATE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Using the new evaluation of the S-factor",
                "curve, the thermonuclear reaction rate of 3He(a,g)7Be",
                "was calculated for the relevant temperature range of",
                "Big Bang nucleosynthesis."
              ]
            }
          ],
